This is a mirror of http://www.vim.org/scripts/script.php?script_id=4835

microViche (microfiche + Vi) lets you pan and zoom through text archives ...

... and has great mouse support,
... automatic mapping,
... a youtube demo (http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=xkED6Mv_4bc),
... and a github site (https://github.com/q335r49/microviche)!

(The original name was 'textabyss')
